# Employee Class


1) Fields
    - Name(string)
    - ID(int)
    - Salary(Decimal)
    - Department(string)
    - hireDate(DateTime)


2) Properties
    - Name(read-only)
    - ID(read-only)
    - Salary(read-only)
    - Department(read-only)
    - hireDate(read-only)
   

3) Constructors
    - Takes Name, ID, Salary, Department
    - Make a Clear Validation
    - Setting hireDate to the CurrentDate


4) Methods
    - GiveSalaryRaise(percentage, managerPassword) "Increases salary"
	- Validates manager password ("mgr123")
	- Validates percentage (0-100)
	- Updates salary
    - ChangeDepartment(newDept, hrPassword) "Changes department"
	- Validates HR password ("hr456")
	- Validates department not empty
	- Updates department
    - DisplayInfo() "Shows employee details"
  
  
5) Static
    - TotalEmployees (static int) "counts total employees"
    - GetTotalEmployees() "static method"


